high_descs: turn around and walk over to the fridge up ahead, then turn left and walk over to the stove up ahead
grab a pan off of the back right burner of the stove there
turn around and walk over to the fridge again
place the pan inside of the fridge to cool then take it back out
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the end of the room again, turn left to face the kitchen counter space there
place the pan down on top of the kitchen counter space
anns.task_desc: place a cooled off pan on top of the kitchen counter space

high_descs: Turn around, go halfway across the room, turn left and go to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick the pan back up.
Turn to the left, go across the room, turn left, go to the door and turn left.
Put the pan on the counter in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward and hang a left to get to the stove.
Pick up the pan directly behind the teapot on the stovetop.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn left and walk around the counter to the other side.
Set the pan down on the counter by the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan from the stovetop to put on the countertop.
